      "description": "This car is in poor condition. The exterior has multiple scratches, dents, and visible body damage across several panels. The interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and scuffed surfaces throughout. The engine runs but has noticeable issues that will require attention.",
      "price": 5000.0,
